{"tid":2470191,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[箍牙]傳統金屬vs透明隱適美invisalign","createTime":"2021-03-31T18:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T09:16:18.000Z","uid":68125,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"15d471e7cad4752b790788c5744fe73b782e8305","tid":2470191,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T18:19:11.000Z","msg":"小妹由細到大都係哨咗兩隻門牙 即係兔仔牙 但令我一直好在意好想去箍牙 中線有啲斜 於是就去咗搵專科牙醫諗住開始矯正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇咗尖沙咀同旺中果間 佢哋講嘅嘢幾乎一樣 俾咗兩個方案我<br />\n<br />\n方案1: 傳統鋼箍剝牙<br />\n<br />\n如果我剝小臼齒, 最後剝牙個位會有好大嘅牙縫,因為我個CASE唔需要咁多位,咁我當然唔想啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢話我個case用金屬箍剝牙又太誇張 於是就俾咗第二個方案我<br />\n<br />\n方案2:隱形牙箍磨牙<br />\n<br />\n佢話效果同鋼箍一樣<br />\n貴過鋼箍少少<br />\n雖然我唔想剝牙<br />\n但自問自制力真係冇咁好...完全靠自己自律戴足22個鐘先有相同效果 都係一年半載 好驚中途堅持唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加好糾結唔知點揀好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99db3ffa84355498905351eb440dae45309ef90e","tid":2470191,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15d471e7cad4752b790788c5744fe73b782e8305","tid":2470191,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T18:19:11.000Z","msg":"小妹由細到大都係哨咗兩隻門牙 即係兔仔牙 但令我一直好在意好想去箍牙 中線有啲斜 於是就去咗搵專科牙醫諗住開始矯正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇咗尖沙咀同旺中果間 佢哋講嘅嘢幾乎一樣 俾咗兩個方案我<br />\n<br />\n方案1: 傳統鋼箍剝牙<br />\n<br />\n如果我剝小臼齒, 最後剝牙個位會有好大嘅牙縫,因為我個CASE唔需要咁多位,咁我當然唔想啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢話我個case用金屬箍剝牙又太誇張 於是就俾咗第二個方案我<br />\n<br />\n方案2:隱形牙箍磨牙<br />\n<br />\n佢話效果同鋼箍一樣<br />\n貴過鋼箍少少<br />\n雖然我唔想剝牙<br />\n但自問自制力真係冇咁好...完全靠自己自律戴足22個鐘先有相同效果 都係一年半載 好驚中途堅持唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加好糾結唔知點揀好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T18:19:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9d52d249e686ff8db1cb3dd3a4b2fb463a5282","tid":2470191,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T18:23:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c35414a553aa62e94d33378985a51fda8df03cec","tid":2470191,"uid":207497,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T18:28:23.000Z","msg":"多數箍隱形嘅人<br />\n最後係要箍多次傳統<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f805d677c45660a8e9f6c4e389d4923902217cb","tid":2470191,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c35414a553aa62e94d33378985a51fda8df03cec","tid":2470191,"uid":207497,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T18:28:23.000Z","msg":"多數箍隱形嘅人<br />\n最後係要箍多次傳統<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T18:36:48.000Z","msg":"唔夠力？佢哋嘅case係咩程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e7a3143024e10a4e391790f7f2742dcada89ac","tid":2470191,"uid":339272,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T18:53:07.000Z","msg":"用傳統鋼箍剝牙<br />\n<br />\n最後塊面瘦左v左"},{"pid":"f74afb7168ebfe121bc8806d4713e5ce60f46013","tid":2470191,"uid":68125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T10:11:17.000Z","msg":"但係鋼箍會唔會冇得打車輪同含撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bbef3b28f96b515f4a2ed215d65a9ba8624bb09","tid":2470191,"uid":70399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T10:14:10.000Z","msg":"其實隱適美係岩輕微調整 如果好勁先要粒粒<br />\n我會覺得隱適美好d <br />\nCool粒粒真係柒好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a70548b450ab863458dfae371663df180a8f84b","tid":2470191,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bbef3b28f96b515f4a2ed215d65a9ba8624bb09","tid":2470191,"uid":70399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-0