46,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T20:33:59.000Z","msg":"箍隱適美唔可能成日食野<br />\n但習慣左就無乜野<br />\n傳統箍清潔有排你清"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T04:15:16.000Z","msg":"箍左後會覺得食野又要除箍擦牙一大堆野<br />\n食兩粒糖依d唔值得花咁多功夫<br />\n淨係食正餐"},{"pid":"b40b40702fa53eb92253e8d216c4affcd5baaad9","tid":2470191,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"303f80d6f09d58aba324a58198304afec3028fbf","tid":2470191,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"babd3e11cb0f813e92f61717cc71479187afacaf","tid":2470191,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T20:33:59.000Z","msg":"箍隱適美唔可能成日食野<br />\n但習慣左就無乜野<br />\n傳統箍清潔有排你清"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T04:05:19.000Z","msg":"為咗對得住幾皮野都會自律到嘅 但每日得兩個鐘食野...咁食唔到幾多 仲要最少一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T08:09:20.000Z","msg":"如果出街食野就麻煩d<br />\n食完又要刷牙<br />\n除左水唔可以飲其他野<br />\n無得食咖哩星米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但後期除左有好多色素的飲品外<br />\n照飲茶了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1fa470eb44d5d8caa959ba50e4443e25859305","tid":2470191,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f50bf0b480d9591cab5dbf1479dc243e3c6e564","tid":2470191,"uid":46933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"babd3e11cb0f813e92f61717cc71479187afacaf","tid":2470191,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T20:33:59.000Z","msg":"箍隱適美唔可能成日食野<br />\n但習慣左就無乜野<br />\n傳統箍清潔有排你清"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T04:15:16.000Z","msg":"箍左後會覺得食野又要除箍擦牙一大堆野<br />\n食兩粒糖依d唔值得花咁多功夫<br />\n淨係食正餐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T08:11:21.000Z","msg":"含hi-chew有d味咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果好為食就唔好箍隱適美<br />\n但箍鋼線食野d渣卡在鐵線都有排清<br />\n<br />\n清潔的時間成本黎講都係箍隱適美"},{"pid":"e7ff78b41e9b1992541be2e1f31c387d64143cf0","tid":2470191,"uid":382064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T06:30:21.000Z","msg":"我以前都係嚴重兔仔牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚴重到要合埋個口都要用力<br />\n我係箍傳統個隻不過係用透明粒粒<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bk72mHW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBk72mHW.png&h=6fc91331&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然呢隻透明比傳統金屬個隻更難keep,不過其實冇想像中咁難<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">最基本早晚刷牙，用牙縫擦同冇酒精漱口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我兩年黎淨係做呢啲已經冇問題，所以唔需要特別擔心清潔問題</span><br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得金屬好核突可以問下醫生有冇得用我上面張相個隻，一開始箍朋友都唔覺"},{"pid":"2b32fa22d799c691aecca93b3c6602e24ac02bdb","tid":2470191,"uid":88486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"早排做完consult, 傳統加剝4隻牙要4萬幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4c9563693d14570ecda282ac960b224419dadb","tid":2470191,"uid":133185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a70548b450ab863458dfae371663df180a8f84b","tid":2470191,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bbef3b28f96b515f4a2ed215d65a9ba8624bb09","tid":2470191,"uid":70399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T10:14:10.000Z","msg":"其實隱適美係岩輕微調整 如果好勁先要粒粒<br />\n我會覺得隱適美好d <br />\nCool粒粒真係柒好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T10:23:11.000Z","msg":"我又唔係話輕微到唔覺眼果種 只係合得埋口 放鬆就會露出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T17:15:08.000Z","msg":"無論用邊隻都好，箍果陣會仲柒d，個嘴會仲突d，不過值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de077a0f84c0559b75583431c0bf987b3b0b31ee","tid":2470191,"uid":117090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b32fa22d799c691aecca93b3c6602e24ac02bdb","tid":2470191,"uid":88486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T16:43: